 base of the fan, which has a tendency to break easily during assembly if you are not careful."]},"id":"8027006e-0f5b-484f-8ce4-5d2d9bb1ef5a","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Design &amp; Functionality"},"id":"0afc6223-016c-4e51-b52d-3b3fa9a8ab4f","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["The Honeywell Fresh Breeze includes a five-year warranty, which is much longer than the standard warranty and can be helpful if you have problems with your fan. The Honeywell customer support team is helpful and generally responds to emails within 24 hours. You can contact Honeywell by phone or email, but a live chat option is not available. You can download the user manual and access a FAQs page on Honeywell&#39;s website as well."]},"id":"d14b62dc-8a85-4cb1-89d8-b4401545a00a","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"8bdd86fa-355e-4c65-8192-5ae01b30f4f8","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["The Honeywell Fresh Breeze HY-048BP has many features that make it one of the best tower fans, including adjustable height, fine temperature control and a dynamic breeze mode. Its construction is a bit flimsy compared to other tower fans, but its cooling power is great for small and average-sized rooms."]},"id":"74cafc91-04a5-41b4-8455-9b3f17c60e08","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_59956","url":"/honeywell-fresh-breeze-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"noel-case","url":"/author/noel-case","dateCreated":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","name":"Noel Case","dateModified":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","id":"dnkqY9NHDMuLpWuEq2JyYX","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2014-07-08T22:04:01Z","datePublished":"2014-07-08T22:04:01Z","name":"Honeywell Fresh Breeze HY-048BP","synopsis":"Editor’s Note: This product has been removed from our side-by-side comparison because it has been discontinued.","review":{"rating":88,"verdict":"The Honeywell Fresh Breeze is a full-featured tower fan and one of the best budget choic